Game Development 1 Assignments:
* Write a command line game of your choice. Something simple without a lot of animations or color needed.

Suggestions:
Mastermind
Tic-Tac-Toe
3d Tic Tac Toe
Connect 4
Sudoku
Minesweeper
Hangman
Word Search
Game of Life
Cryptographic Cipher Encoder/Decoder
Flash cards quiz game
Base converter
Metric to Imperial converter
Matching game (guess two cards on the board until you find pairs)
Go Fish
War
Othello


* Use Processing to create a visualization of the game.

* Mentor request: Let me know which resources helped you get started with Processing (tutorials on placing pixels, getting mouse input, etc). Add to the brainstorm list of possible games. Thanks!